name: Burger
desciption: Burger King advertises the Whopper as Americas Favorite Burger and theres no doubting its iconic status. More than 11 million customers walk through Burger Kings doors each day, many of them in pursuit of the famous burger.

name: Chicken breast
desciption: Chicken breast is low in fat and calories but extremely high in protein. It’s a great source of many nutrients. Again, feel free to eat fattier cuts of chicken if you’re not eating that many carbs.

name: KFC Chicken
desciption: KFCs Original Recipe Chicken is famous for its secret 11 herbs and spices and for launching the brand into fast food superstardom.

name: Taco Bell
desciption: Taco Bell has crowned this burrito "The Supreme Ruler of the Burrito Empire," and it has many loyal subjects to prove it.

name: Chick-fil-A
desciption: Chick-fil-A may be politically polarizing, but people tend to have a unified stance on their original Chicken Sandwich: "delicious."

name: If Dunkin
desciption: If Dunkin is trying to pivot away from the doughnut world, Krispy Kreme will hold down the fort.

name: Culvers
desciption: Ask anyone what Culvers is famous for and theyll tell you: the ButterBurger. The fast-food chain has nicknamed it

name: McDonalds Happy Meal
desciption: The McDonalds Happy Meal has been thriving since 1979, thanks to its kid-sized portions, colorful signature packaging, and of course, the collectible toys.

name: White Castle
desciption: White Castle has been serving sliders since 1921, when the restaurant became Americas first fast-food burger chain. Today, sliders remain the most popular item on the menu.

name: Roast beef
desciption: Featuring only two ingredients, roast beef and a sesame seed bun, Arbys claims that this is the sandwich that put roast beef on the map.
